## Function to find 4th highest value 
oz4th<-function(x){
  y<-sort(x,na.last=F)
  an4th<-y[length(y)-3]
}
##
##  Function to calculate 3 year rolling averages
three_year_rolling_av <- function(x) {
  n <- length(x)
  y <- rep(NA, n-2)
  for (k in 3:n) {
    y[k-2] <- mean(x[(k-2):k])
  }
  y
}
